dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents hydrography for Waukesha County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waukesha_HydroPoly_2014.gdb.

overview.eaover: [The features within the digital planimetric map products are differentiated by any combination of Microstation symbology characteristics including, Level, Weight, Style and Color. All features are stored as either point, line or area features, none of which have any associated database attribution assigned. Files are structured with a naming convention of PLANttrr.dgn where tt=township, rr=range,.]
